						<p><div class="item">
<h2><a class="listing" style="link" href="/en/Dossiers/S-T-Issues/Water/Related-developments/Thirty-five-water-conservation-methods-for-agriculture-farming-and-gardening" title="Thirty-five water conservation methods for agriculture, farming, and gardening " alt="link">Thirty-five water conservation methods for agriculture, farming, and gardening </a></h2>

	
					<p>This four-part article by Big Picture Agriculture provides a list of 35 different water conservation methods that are ideal for small and medium sized farms and gardens. Some of the methods described are adapted to drier climates, others to higher altitude cultivation, though most apply to climatic conditions and crops found in ACP countries.&nbsp;(<a href="http://www.bigpictureagriculture.com/2013/02/thirty-five-water-conservation-methods-agriculture-farming-gardening-323.html" target="_blank">Big Picture Agriculture</a>, 02/2012)&nbsp;</p>
