						<p><div class="item">
<h2><a class="listing" style="link" href="/en/Dossiers/S-T-Issues/Water/Related-developments/Using-wastewater-as-fertilizer" title="Using wastewater as fertilizer" alt="link">Using wastewater as fertilizer</a></h2>

	
					<p>Sewage sludge, wastewater and liquid manure are valuable sources of fertilizer for food production. Fraunhofer researchers have now developed a chemical-free, eco-friendly process that enables the recovered salts to be converted directly into organic food for crop plants. Struvite fertilizer recovered from wastewater is a high-quality product that slowly releases nutrients into the soil. The innovative process precipitates out the nutrients in a form that enables them to be directly applied as fertilizer. It is also suitable for wastewaters from the food-industry and from the production of biogas from agricultural wastes. The only prerequisite is that the process water should be rich in ammonium and phosphates.(Physorg, 3/8/2012)<a href="http://phys.org/news/2012-08-wastewater-fertilizer.html" target="_blank">http://phys.org/news/2012-08-wastewater-fertilizer.html</a></p>
							<p><span class="date">26/09/2012</span></p>
	<div class="cnt">
	<a class="link" href="/en/Dossiers/S-T-Issues/Water/Related-developments/Using-wastewater-as-fertilizer">Read more...</a>
</div>
<br class="cl">
</div>
</p>
						
						<p><div class="item">
<h2><a class="listing" style="link" href="/en/Dossiers/S-T-Issues/Water/Related-developments/Kenya-maps-out-new-areas-for-irrigation" title="Kenya maps out new areas for irrigation" alt="link">Kenya maps out new areas for irrigation</a></h2>

	
					<p>The Kenyan Ministry of water and irrigation is in the process of mapping out areas across the country where irrigation schemes will be undertaken in the next 18 years. It is currently surveying all regions in the country to identify the areas where irrigation projects are needed to consolidate food security.(Via AllAfrica, 2/8/2012)<a href="http://allafrica.com/stories/201208021276.html" target="_blank">http://allafrica.com/stories/201208021276.html</a></p>
							<p><span class="date">26/09/2012</span></p>
	<div class="cnt">
	<a class="link" href="/en/Dossiers/S-T-Issues/Water/Related-developments/Kenya-maps-out-new-areas-for-irrigation">Read more...</a>
